  p We have created the Platform for the purpose of providing editorial content, software and other content and features that we believe our users will use and enjoy, and while we are always doing our best to monitor the information on the Platform and to update the Platform regularly, we cannot guarantee the accuracy, currency, reliability or completeness of any information or material included here, or on any site accessible from here. We expect that you will use your own skill and care in using the Platform and in communicating with our business partners and with other users, and in relying on any information or participating in any events or other opportunities that may be available from the Platform. In order to use or access the Platform, you must review and agree to our Terms of Use, which include this Policy and which also include important terms regarding the materials that we and our business partners and users may make available on or through the Platform.

  p WE DO NOT PRE-SCREEN OR APPROVE USERS, AND WE CANNOT GUARANTEE USER IDENTITIES OR ANY INFORMATION THAT USERS PROVIDE. WE HAVE NO RESPONSIBILITY OR LIABILITY FOR ANY ACTIONS YOU MAY TAKE ON OR IN CONNECTION WITH THE PLATFORM. YOU SHOULD NOT PROVIDE ANY PERSONALLY IDENTIFIABLE INFORMATION TO ANY OTHER USER UNLESS YOU KNOW WHO THAT USER IS AND KNOW WHAT HE OR SHE INTENDS TO DO WITH YOUR PERSONALLY IDENTIFIABLE INFORMATION. SIMILARLY, YOU SHOULD NOT PROVIDE ANY PERSONALLY IDENTIFIABLE INFORMATION TO OUR VENDORS OR BUSINESS PARTNERS WITHOUT CONFIRMING THE IDENTITIES OF THOSE VENDORS OR BUSINESS PARTNERS AND REVIEWING THE PRIVACY POLICIES THAT THEY HAVE IN EFFECT. FINALLY, YOU SHOULD NOT PROVIDE ANY PERSONALLY IDENTIFIABLE TO US UNLESS YOU HAVE READ AND ARE COMFORTABLE WITH ALL OF THE TERMS OF THIS POLICY AND OUT TERMS OF USE AND HAVE NO OBJECTIONS TO THE WAYS IN WHICH WE PROPOSE TO USE YOUR PERSONALLY IDENTIFIABLE INFORMATION.